description: Try our easy to follow Fish Tacos recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Fish Tacos Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 2 tbs leftover fennel pickle (see Barbecued whole barramundi recipe)

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 180Â°C. Heat taco shells according to packet instructions.
Combine avocado, tomato, onion, lemon juice and 1 tbs oil in a bowl. Season to taste
Heat remaining oil in a frying pan over medium heat. Add barramundi, parsley and paprika and cook, tossing, for 2 minutes or until heated through.
Fill taco shells with lettuce, barramundi, tomato salsa, fennel pickle, if using, and finish with a dollop of sour cream. Serve with lime wedges.
